videos.description: Isaiah Thomas is able to get the fadeaway shot to go over the bigger Robin Lopez.
videos.headline: Thomas nails fadeaway over Lopez

videos.description: Jae Crowder pumps up the crowd after hitting a 3-pointer against the Bulls, resulting in a Chicago timeout.
videos.headline: Crowder pumped up after 3-pointer

videos.description: Tyler Zeller drives the lane and dunks it over Robin Lopez.

videos.headline: Tyler Zeller throws it down over Lopez

videos.description: Jae Crowder limps to the locker room after stepping on Rajon Rondo's foot.
videos.headline: Crowder limps to locker room

videos.description: Dwyane Wade gets the steal and takes it himself for the layup at the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Wade steals it from Thomas, finishes with layup) 2016/11/02

videos.headline: Wade steals it from Thomas, finishes with layup

videos.description: Amir Johnson hits his fourth 3-pointer of the night against the Bulls, with Isaiah Thomas getting the steal and layup on the ensuing possession.

videos.headline: Amir Johnson brings TD Garden to its feet with his fourth 3-pointer

videos.description: Amir Johnson's big night continues with a nifty hook shot against the Bulls.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Amir Johnson sinks sweeping hook shot) 2016/11/02

videos.headline: Amir Johnson sinks sweeping hook shot

videos.description: After several misses shots, the Bulls finally break through thanks to Bobby Ports who gets the layup to go.
videos.headline: Hustle pays off for Bulls

videos.description: Isaiah Thomas hits a ridiculous reverse layup for two crucial Celtics points.
videos.headline: Circus shot falls for Thomas

videos.description: Isaiah Thomas speaks with Doris Burke about the Celtics holding off the Bulls late and Amir Johnson's big night.
